boofcv.alg.feature.disparity

Class DisparitySparseScoreSadRect<ArrayData,Input extends boofcv.struct.image.ImageGray>

  • java.lang.Object
    • boofcv.alg.feature.disparity.DisparitySparseScoreSadRect<ArrayData,Input>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImplDisparitySparseScoreSadRect_F32, ImplDisparitySparseScoreSadRect_S16, ImplDisparitySparseScoreSadRect_U8

    public abstract class DisparitySparseScoreSadRect<ArrayData,Input extends boofcv.struct.image.ImageGray>
extends java.lang.Object
    Computes disparity SAD scores using a rectangular region at the specified points only along the x-axis. Scores are returned in an array where the index refers to the disparity.

      • DisparitySparseScoreSadRect

        public DisparitySparseScoreSadRect(int minDisparity,
                                   int maxDisparity,
                                   int radiusX,
                                   int radiusY)
        Configures disparity calculation.
        Parameters:
        minDisparity - Minimum disparity that it will consider. Must be ≥ 0 && < maxDisparity
        maxDisparity - Maximum disparity that it will calculate. Must be > 0
        radiusX - Radius of the rectangular region along x-axis.
        radiusY - Radius of the rectangular region along y-axis.

        public abstract ArrayData getScore()
